* 台灣捷爾東事業開發股份有限公司 - 經營訪日旅行服務，同時提供JR東日本集團車站及周邊開發的技術，車站構內、車站便當、旅館等開發。<ref name="JR東日本砸2700萬在台設分支！">{{Cite web |url=https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/fncnews/life/28730 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-09-01 |archive-date=2021-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215214719/https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/fncnews/life/28730 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 英國 {{le|West Midlands Trains}} - 15%。<ref name="WestMid">[https://www.abellio.com/sites/default/files/downloads/170810_press_release_west_midlands_trains_announced_as_winning_bidder.pdf West Midlands Trains announced as winning bidder for West Midlands franchise] {{Wayback|url=https://www.abellio.com/sites/default/files/downloads/170810_press_release_west_midlands_trains_announced_as_winning_bidder.pdf |date=20170810130543 }} Abellio 10 August 2017</ref> （[[荷蘭鐵路|荷蘭鐵路]]子公司 {{le|Abellio|Abellio (transport company)}} 70%、[[三井物產|三井物產]] 15%）

